1
00:00:03,503 --> 00:00:04,505
<i>We have an emergency!</i>

2
00:00:04,588 --> 00:00:08,217
<i>Suspicious figures with knives</i>
<i>have appeared on the festival platform!</i>

3
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:11,887
